 Conversation 2 ---\nQuestion: there are sides of me who think that i play it safe for me, but for others it would seem like im taking risk by not betting on everyone\'s bets\nAnswer: 1. Do you enjoy trying new things and experiencing new things, or do you prefer to stick with what you know and are comfortable with?\n\n\n--- Conversation 3 ---\nQuestion: trying new experiences\nAnswer: 1. Do you consider yourself to be more logical and analytical, or more creative and intuitive?\n\n\n--- Conversation 4 ---\nQuestion: all of the above\nAnswer: 1. Are you more of a "big picture" thinker, or do you focus more on the details?\n\n\n--- Conversation 5 ---\nQuestion: i can get into the details, but i prefer the big picture\nAnswer: 1. Do you enjoy being in leadership roles, or do you prefer to follow and support others in leadership? [/INST]', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=0, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=100, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None, extra_args=None), prompt_token_ids: None, prompt_embeds shape: None, lora_request: None, prompt_adapter_request: None.
